    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Dual Wielding Sphere, Spherecasting.</p>\n<p><strong>Benefit:</strong> As a special attack action, while you have martial focus you can use your Dual Attack or Combo Maneuvers ability with a sphere ability in place of your first offhand weapon attack. The ability must be one that requires a touch attack or that can be made with a weapon attack and that can be cast with a standard action. The sphere ability has its caster level (excluding enhancement bonuses) limited to your BAB and provokes attacks of opportunity normally.</p>\n<p>If the sphere ability is a ranged attack, it does not provoke an attack of opportunity if you possess the Mixed Assault talent.</p>\n",
